---
title: Mozzarella and Courgette Pizza with rocket and crushed pepper topping
description: This veggie pizza has a lot to shout about. Perfectly charred courgette, melted cheddar cheese, and if that's not enough, a sprinkling of creamy mozzarella to top it all off.
